{"tid":845354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張彪告陳祥富事件？的士司機被捕後死亡案 參與拘捕警員作供","createTime":"2018-10-02T14:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T14:49:56.000Z","uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e70a234552655a4cc7500d87b715d0b55a2b0b9b","tid":845354,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:39:41.000Z","msg":"65歲的士司機陳輝旺被警方拘捕期間不適，及後不治，死因庭展開研訊。死者長女作供稱，父親跟她說被警員打。有份參與拘捕的警員作供則指，陳輝旺不斷掙扎，期間要把他按在地上鎖上手銬。<br />\n<br />\n死者陳輝旺的妻子及兩名女兒到西九龍裁判法院的死因庭出席聆訊，兩名西隧職員亦到庭作供。事發在2012年11月11日，警方在西隧九龍出口以涉嫌襲擊拘捕的士司機陳輝旺，期間他不適送院，一個月後不治。<br />\n<br />\n陳輝旺的長女作供時指，到醫院探望父親時發現父親身上有多處傷痕，頸有瘀傷，父親向她說「被警員打」。而醫生指其父親因頸椎受傷致四肢癱瘓，而頸傷一定是外力造成，磁力共振結果顯示父親頸骨移位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/的士司機被捕後死亡案-參與拘捕警員作供-132840752.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%BE%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%A1%88-%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B-132840752.html&d=SxPt8DG1YEC6sfKZV8wkZv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f8b37056\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/的士司機被捕後死亡案-參與拘捕警員作供-132840752.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/223926_b29ebee74f0b710891cdc9701af2ba6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F223926_b29ebee74f0b710891cdc9701af2ba6a.png&h=2b6dc0a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56bba4148d6aad677c0e393e05bc629bacdb1c10","tid":845354,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/224935_e5259ae1ef1c7a5f21483c8af564eb30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F224935_e5259ae1ef1c7a5f21483c8af564eb30.png&h=7af1e9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/224949_5caa96b37419aaaa9793ddece8574649.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F224949_5caa96b37419aaaa9793ddece8574649.png&h=da208e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好應景"}]}